*{{cite web|title=Sudden stops in the Eurozone|author1-first=Jean|author1-last=Pisani-Ferry|author1-link=Jean Pisani-Ferry|author2-first=Silvia|author2-last=Merler|url=http://www.voxeu.org/article/public-capital-flows-replacing-private-flows-eurozone-what-it-means-policy|publisher=[[Centre for Economic Policy Research#VoxEU.org|Vox]]|date=April 2, 2012}}
